  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink22-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> kaḷaviṉiṟ puṇarntu piṉpu varaintukoṇṭu oḻukāniṉṟa talaimakaṟkup
          puṟattoḻukkam uḷatāyiṟṟāka, āṟṟāḷākiya talaimakaḷ tōḻikkuc colliyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink22">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> aḷḷa lāṭiya puḷḷik kaḷvaṉ</l>
          <l> muḷḷi vēraḷaic cellu mūra</l>
          <l> ṉalla colli maṇantiṉi</l>
          <l> nīyē ṉeṉṟa tevaṉko laṉṉāy.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> The man from the village</l>
          <l rend='indent2'> where the spotted crab that played in the mire </l>
          <l rend='indent2'> goes [back] into [its] hole at the Muḷḷi roots – </l>
          <l> That, after speaking good [words] [and] uniting [with me], he said</l>
          <l rend='indent4'> “Now I won’t leave [you anymore].”</l> 
            <l> What [of it], mother?</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
